            "| `triage_priority_badge_reward_loop_candidate` | `SCREENSHOT_CANDIDATE_DECISION_MATRIX_KO.md` | `A/B 판정`, `promoted_candidate` | `P0_WAIT_EXTERNAL_AB` | 최우선 후보는 `12_career_record_next_objective.png`를 유지하고 승격 전 보류 사유를 남김 |\n" +
            "| `screenshot_ab_loop_response_count` | `SCREENSHOT_CANDIDATE_AB_TEST_KO.md` | `screenshot_ab_loop_response_count` | `" + responseCount + "` | 응답 5건 이상이면 승격 후보 검토로 전환 |\n" +
            "| `screenshot_ab_loop_understanding_comment_count` | `SCREENSHOT_CANDIDATE_AB_TEST_KO.md` | `screenshot_ab_loop_understanding_comment_count` | `" + understandingCommentCount + "` | 루프 이해 코멘트 5건 이상이면 `post_external_collection_promotion_summary` 판정에 반영 |\n" +
            "| `screenshot_ab_loop_collection_status` | `SCREENSHOT_CANDIDATE_AB_TEST_KO.md` | `screenshot_ab_loop_collection_status` | `" + collectionStatus + "` | `waiting_for_screenshot_ab_loop_responses`이면 Store Presence 업로드 전 후보 승격 보류 |\n\n" +
            "## 우선순위 배지 외부 회수 후 처리 상태\n\n" +
            "| priority_badge_id | after_collection_status | manual_update_target | completion_gate | next_action |\n" +
            "| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n" +
            "| `triage_priority_badge_reward_loop_candidate` | `P0_WAIT_EXTERNAL_AB` | `selected_upload_set`, `promoted_candidate`, `post_external_collection_promotion_summary` | `external_5_and_ab_loop_5_and_understanding_5` | `12_career_record_next_objective.png` 후보 유지, 회수 충족 후 승격 검토 |\n" +
            "| `triage_priority_badge_main_menu_baseline` | `P1_BASELINE_GUARD` | `01_main_menu.png`, `main_menu_loop_entry`, `menu_campaign_briefing_weakness`, `STORE_PRESENCE_SELECTION_KO.md` | `main_menu_loop_entry_response_collected`; `menu_campaign_briefing_weakness_response_collected` | 기준 화면 유지/교체 판단과 추천 회차 브리핑/직전 약점 보정 초점 이해도를 A/B 응답과 대조 |\n" +
            "| `triage_priority_badge_copy_alignment` | `P1_COPY_ALIGNMENT_COLLECT` | `achievement_career_copy_alignment`, `lowResolutionReleaseCopyAlignmentReadable`, `careerRecordActionHintReadable`, `storeCandidateMentionsBriefingRetrospective=true` | `copy_alignment_comment_collected` | 성과 목표 힌트와 캠페인 기록 다음 목표/브리핑 회고 문구 일치 여부를 수동 기록 |\n\n" +
            BuildStorePresencePriorityBadgeAfterCollectionStatusMarkdown() +
            BuildStorePresenceAbTodoMappingMarkdown() +
            "## 입력 절차\n\n" +
            "1. Steamworks Store Presence에 상점 문구와 공식 스크린샷 8장을 입력한다.\n" +
            "2. 캡슐 이미지와 트레일러 업로드 파일이 `Builds/Steamworks/v0.3.0/store_page`의 선택 manifest와 일치하는지 확인한다.\n" +
            "3. 후보 스크린샷은 바로 업로드하지 않고, `SCREENSHOT_CANDIDATE_DECISION_MATRIX_KO.md`와 SHA manifest 기준으로 비교 검수만 한다.\n" +
            "4. 입력 후 `Evidence/STORE_PRESENCE.md`에 상점, 스크린샷, 캡슐, 트레일러, SHA manifest, A/B 판정, 판단 복기 패턴 분포, 판단 복기 진행 HUD, 브리핑 회고 후보 입력란, 토스트 UI 캡처, `selected_upload_set`, `promoted_candidate` 확인 증거를 남긴다.\n\n" +
            "## STORE_PRESENCE.md 작성 완료 전 자체점검\n\n" +
            "| 항목 | STORE_PRESENCE.md 입력란 | 완료 기준 |\n" +
            "| --- | --- | --- |\n" +
            "| Steamworks URL/화면 캡처 | `Steamworks URL/화면 캡처` | 실제 Store Presence 화면 캡처 경로를 적는다. |\n" +
            "| SHA 확인 | `SHA 확인` | `STORE_CANDIDATE_CAPTURE_SYNC_HASHES.sha256` 확인 결과를 적는다. |\n" +
            "| 공식/승격 후보 | `selected_upload_set`, `promoted_candidate` | 현재 공식 8장 또는 승격 후보 상태를 적는다. |\n" +
            "| 14번 복기 후보 | `decision_audit_coaching_candidate_file`, `decision_audit_coaching_candidate_case`, `decision_audit_coaching_candidate_round_trip`, `decision_audit_coaching_hud_evidence`, `decision_audit_coaching_hud_terms` | 14번 파일명, `복기 W-207`, 왕복 QA 키, `care_review_decision_audit_coaching_hud_smoke_result.json`, `reviewHudUpdatesAfterDecision=true`를 적는다. |\n" +
            "| 브리핑 회고 후보 | `briefing_retrospective_candidate_file`, `briefing_retrospective_candidate_terms`, `briefing_retrospective_candidate_smoke` | 12번 파일명, `브리핑 회고`/`예고 위험`/`실제 결과`, smoke 키를 적는다. |\n" +
            "| 토스트 UI 캡처 | `성과 토스트 UI 캡처` | `ACHIEVEMENT_TOAST_UI_CAPTURE.md` 확인 결과를 적는다. |\n" +
            "| A/B 응답 회수 | `screenshot_ab_loop_response_count`, `screenshot_ab_loop_not_collected_count`, `screenshot_ab_loop_collection_status`, `screenshot_ab_loop_understanding_comment_count` | 회수 수치와 보류 상태, 루프 이해 코멘트 수를 적는다. |\n\n" +
            "## 통과 기준\n\n" +
            "- Store Presence 입력 세트가 제출안과 `STORE_PRESENCE_SELECTION_KO.md`에 일치한다.\n" +
            "- A/B 판정 manifest와 Store Presence 통합 선택 manifest의 추천 후보가 같은 파일명으로 일치한다.\n" +
            "- 판단 복기 보조 후보는 `decision_audit_coaching_candidate_evidence`, `14_case_archive_decision_audit_coaching_focus.png`, `복기 W-207`, `caseArchiveDecisionAuditCoachingButtonOpensFirstUseCase=true`, `caseArchiveDecisionAuditCoachingReturnOpensCareerRecord=true`, `" + DecisionAuditCoachingHudStoreCandidateSummary + "`로 추적된다.\n" +
            "- 성과-캠페인 루프 A/B 질문은 플레이테스트 요청서, 수동 회수 인덱스 템플릿, 자동 집계 CSV에 같은 `screenshot_ab_loop_*` 축으로 연결되어 있고 `achievement_career_copy_alignment` 문구 일치 질문과 `menu_campaign_briefing_weakness` 추천 회차 브리핑/직전 약점 보정 초점 질문을 포함한다.\n" +
            "- 브리핑 회고 상점 후보 근거는 `briefing_retrospective_candidate_evidence`, `briefing_retrospective_candidate_file`, `briefing_retrospective_candidate_terms`, `briefing_retrospective_candidate_smoke`, `storeCandidateMentionsBriefingRetrospective=true`, `브리핑 회고`, `예고 위험`, `실제 결과`, `12_career_record_next_objective.png`로 Store Presence 입력 전 확인하고 `Evidence/STORE_PRESENCE.md`에 별도 기록한다.\n" +
            "- A/B 응답 회수 수치와 승격 보류 사유는 Store Presence 입력 전 `waiting_for_screenshot_ab_loop_responses` 상태로 확인되고 `Evidence/STORE_PRESENCE.md` 입력란과 release candidate JSON `memberSummary=storePresenceEvidenceBundle.checks.memberSummary`에 같은 축으로 기록된다.\n" +
            "- 판단 복기 패턴 분포는 `care_review_playtest_aggregate.json`/Markdown과 Store/QA handoff 요약에 함께 연결되어 있다.\n" +
            "- 보정 후보 결과 확인 단계가 상점 제출안, 제출 전 자체점검, Store Presence 통합 선택 manifest에 모두 연결되어 있다.\n" +
            "- `STORE_CANDIDATE_CAPTURE_SYNC_HASHES.sha256`가 handoff와 Steamworks 루트에 있고 후보 PNG 파일명이 모두 있다.\n" +
            "- `ACHIEVEMENT_TOAST_UI_CAPTURE.md`가 handoff와 Steamworks 루트에 있고 성과 토스트 UI 캡처가 읽을 수 있는 상태다.\n" +
            "- 후보 이미지 승격은 실제 사람 회수/A/B 기준 충족 전까지 보류한다.\n" +
            "- 증거 노트에는 필수 키워드 `상점`, `스크린샷`, `캡슐`, `트레일러`, `SHA`, `A/B`, `판단 복기 패턴 분포`, `토스트 UI 캡처`, `selected_upload_set`, `promoted_candidate`가 포함된다.\n";
    }

    private static string BuildDecisionAuditCoachingAggregateHandoffSummary()
    {
        string aggregateJson = SafeReadAllText("Builds/QA/v0.3.0/playtest_packet/care_review_playtest_aggregate.json");
        int sessionCount = ExtractJsonInt(aggregateJson, "sessionCount");
        int coachingSessionCount = ExtractJsonInt(aggregateJson, "decisionAuditCoachingSessionCount");
        int mismatchCount = ExtractJsonInt(aggregateJson, "decisionAuditCoachingMismatchCount");
        int urgentDelayCount = ExtractJsonInt(aggregateJson, "decisionAuditCoachingUrgentDelayCount");
        int highCostSupportCount = ExtractJsonInt(aggregateJson, "decisionAuditCoachingHighCostSupportCount");
        int appealQueueSessionCount = ExtractJsonInt(aggregateJson, "decisionAuditCoachingAppealQueueSessionCount");
        string topPattern = aggregateJson.Contains("\"고비용 지원\"", StringComparison.Ordinal) ? "고비용 지원" : "패턴 미확인";
        string recommendedMandate = aggregateJson.Contains("\"긴축 감사\"", StringComparison.Ordinal) ? "긴축 감사" : "추천 운영 미확인";
        return "decisionAuditCoachingSessionCount=" + coachingSessionCount + "/" + sessionCount +
            "; decisionAuditCoachingPatternCounts=" + topPattern +
            "; decisionAuditCoachingMandateCounts=" + recommendedMandate +
            "; mismatch=" + mismatchCount +
            "; urgentDelay=" + urgentDelayCount +
            "; highCostSupport=" + highCostSupportCount +
            "; appealQueueSessionCount=" + appealQueueSessionCount;
    }

    private static bool DecisionAuditCoachingAggregateHandoffReady()
    {
        string aggregateJsonPath = "Builds/QA/v0.3.0/playtest_packet/care_review_playtest_aggregate.json";
        string aggregateMarkdownPath = "Builds/QA/v0.3.0/playtest_packet/care_review_playtest_aggregate.md";
        return FileContainsAll(
                aggregateJsonPath,
                "\"decisionAuditCoachingSessionCount\"",
                "\"decisionAuditCoachingPatternCounts\"",
                "\"decisionAuditCoachingMandateCounts\"",
                "\"decisionAuditCoachingAppealQueueSessionCount\"",
                "고비용 지원",
                "긴축 감사") &&
            FileContainsAll(
                aggregateMarkdownPath,
                "판단 복기 패턴 분포",
                "복기 생성 세션",
                "고비용 지원",
                "긴축 감사");
    }

    private static string PackageEvidenceLine(string label, string packagePath, string hashPath)
    {
        long bytes = File.Exists(packagePath) ? new FileInfo(packagePath).Length : 0L;
        string hash = File.Exists(hashPath) ? File.ReadAllText(hashPath, Encoding.UTF8).Trim() : "missing";
        return "- " + label + ": `" + packagePath.Replace("\\", "/") + "`, " + bytes + " bytes, SHA256 `" + hash + "`";
    }

    private static PlaytestCollectionAudit BuildPlaytestCollectionAudit()
    {
        Directory.CreateDirectory(PlaytestCollectionInboxPath);
        Directory.CreateDirectory(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath);

        List<PlaytestSessionAuditRow> rows = new();
        HashSet<string> seenSessionIds = new(StringComparer.OrdinalIgnoreCase);
        AppendPlaytestSessionAuditRows(PlaytestCollectionInboxPath, "external_inbox", rows, seenSessionIds);
        AppendPlaytestSessionAuditRows(PlaytestQaSupportBundleArchivePath, "qa_support_bundle_archive", rows, seenSessionIds);
        AppendPlaytestSessionAuditRows(PlaytestQaSessionArchivePath, "qa_sample_archive", rows, seenSessionIds);
        rows.Sort((left, right) => string.Compare(left.sessionId, right.sessionId, StringComparison.Ordinal));

        PlaytestCollectionAudit audit = new()
        {
            generatedAt = DateTime.Now.ToString("s"),
            auditCompleted = true,
            hasAuditOutputs = true,
            sourceDirectories = PlaytestCollectionInboxPath + ";" + PlaytestQaSessionArchivePath + ";" + PlaytestQaSupportBundleArchivePath,
            sessionCount = rows.Count,
            externalCompleteSessionCount = 0,
            completeSessionCount = 0,
            playableSessionCount = 0,
            surveySessionCount = 0,
            diagnosticSessionCount = 0,
            supportBundleSessionCount = 0,
            supportBundleManifestCount = 0,
            supportBundleRuntimeIssueCount = 0,
            supportBundleExternalHandoffHashCount = 0,
            noLocalPathSessionCount = 0,
            recommendedHumanMinimum = 5,
            recommendedCommercialMinimum = 10,
            rows = rows
        };

        foreach (PlaytestSessionAuditRow row in rows)
        {
            if (row.complete)
            {
                audit.completeSessionCount++;
            }

            if (row.complete && row.source == "external_inbox")
            {
                audit.externalCompleteSessionCount++;
            }

            if (row.hasPlayLogCsv && row.hasPlayLogJson && row.decisionRows >= 35)
            {
                audit.playableSessionCount++;
            }

            if (row.hasSurveyJson && row.hasSurveyMarkdown)
            {
                audit.surveySessionCount++;
            }

            if (row.hasDiagnosticJson && row.hasDiagnosticMarkdown)
            {
                audit.diagnosticSessionCount++;
            }

            if (row.receivedViaSupportBundle)
            {
                audit.supportBundleSessionCount++;
            }

            if (row.hasSupportBundleManifest)
            {
                audit.supportBundleManifestCount++;
            }

            if (row.supportBundleHasRuntimeIssues)
            {
                audit.supportBundleRuntimeIssueCount++;
            }

            if (row.supportBundleHasExternalHandoffHash)
            {
                audit.supportBundleExternalHandoffHashCount++;
            }

            if (row.filesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath)
            {
                audit.noLocalPathSessionCount++;
            }
        }

        audit.readyForBalanceTuning = audit.externalCompleteSessionCount >= audit.recommendedHumanMinimum;
        audit.readyForCommercialTuning = audit.externalCompleteSessionCount >= audit.recommendedCommercialMinimum;
        PopulateCommercialChecklistAggregateCrossCheck(audit);
        PopulateScreenshotAbLoopAggregateCrossCheck(audit);
        PlaytestCommercialTriageReport triage = BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageReport(audit);

        string summaryPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_collection_audit_summary.json");
        string csvPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_collection_audit.csv");
        string markdownPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_collection_audit.md");
        string triageJsonPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_commercial_triage.json");
        string triageCsvPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_commercial_triage.csv");
        string triageActionCsvPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_commercial_triage_actions.csv");
        string triageMarkdownPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_commercial_triage.md");
        string triageHtmlPath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_commercial_triage.html");
        string triageSmokePath = Path.Combine(PlaytestCollectionAuditPath, "care_review_playtest_commercial_triage_smoke_result.json");
        File.WriteAllText(summaryPath, BuildPlaytestCollectionAuditJson(audit), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(csvPath, BuildPlaytestCollectionAuditCsv(audit), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(markdownPath, BuildPlaytestCollectionAuditMarkdown(audit), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(triageJsonPath, BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageJson(triage), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(triageCsvPath, BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageCsv(triage), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(triageActionCsvPath, BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageActionCsv(triage), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(triageMarkdownPath, BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageMarkdown(triage), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(triageHtmlPath, BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageHtml(triage), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        File.WriteAllText(triageSmokePath, BuildPlaytestCommercialTriageSmokeJson(triage), new UTF8Encoding(false));
        AssetDatabase.Refresh();
        return audit;
    }

    private static void AppendPlaytestSessionAuditRows(string sourcePath, string sourceLabel, List<PlaytestSessionAuditRow> rows, HashSet<string> seenSessionIds)
    {
        if (!Directory.Exists(sourcePath))
        {
            return;
        }

        foreach (string sessionPath in Directory.GetDirectories(sourcePath, "CR-*", SearchOption.AllDirectories))
        {
            string sessionId = Path.GetFileName(sessionPath);
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(sessionId) || !seenSessionIds.Add(sessionId))
            {
                continue;
            }

            rows.Add(BuildPlaytestSessionAuditRow(sessionPath, sourceLabel, sessionId));
        }
    }

    private static PlaytestSessionAuditRow BuildPlaytestSessionAuditRow(string sessionPath, string sourceLabel, string sessionId)
    {
        string supportBundlePath = FindSupportBundleRoot(sessionPath);
        bool receivedViaSupportBundle = !string.IsNullOrEmpty(supportBundlePath);
        string supportBundleName = receivedViaSupportBundle ? Path.GetFileName(supportBundlePath) : "";
        string playLogJsonPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_play_log.json");
        string playLogCsvPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_play_log.csv");
        string incidentLogCsvPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_incident_log.csv");
        string summaryJsonPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_playtest_summary.json");
        string feedbackMarkdownPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_playtest_feedback.md");
        string surveyJsonPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_in_game_feedback.json");
        string surveyMarkdownPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_in_game_feedback.md");
        string dashboardPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_analytics_dashboard.html");
        string diagnosticJsonPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_system_diagnostic.json");
        string diagnosticMarkdownPath = Path.Combine(sessionPath, "care_review_system_diagnostic.md");
        string supportBundleManifestJsonPath = receivedViaSupportBundle ? Path.Combine(supportBundlePath, "care_review_support_bundle_manifest.json") : "";
        string supportBundleManifestMarkdownPath = receivedViaSupportBundle ? Path.Combine(supportBundlePath, "care_review_support_bundle_manifest.md") : "";
        string supportBundleRuntimeIssuesJsonPath = receivedViaSupportBundle ? Path.Combine(supportBundlePath, "care_review_runtime_issues.json") : "";
        string supportBundleRuntimeIssuesMarkdownPath = receivedViaSupportBundle ? Path.Combine(supportBundlePath, "care_review_runtime_issues.md") : "";

        string playLogJson = SafeReadAllText(playLogJsonPath);
        string summaryJson = SafeReadAllText(summaryJsonPath);
        string feedbackMarkdown = SafeReadAllText(feedbackMarkdownPath);
        string surveyJson = SafeReadAllText(surveyJsonPath);
        string surveyMarkdown = SafeReadAllText(surveyMarkdownPath);
        string dashboardHtml = SafeReadAllText(dashboardPath);
        string diagnosticJson = SafeReadAllText(diagnosticJsonPath);
        string diagnosticMarkdown = SafeReadAllText(diagnosticMarkdownPath);
        string supportBundleManifestJson = SafeReadAllText(supportBundleManifestJsonPath);
        string supportBundleManifestMarkdown = SafeReadAllText(supportBundleManifestMarkdownPath);
        string supportBundleRuntimeIssuesJson = SafeReadAllText(supportBundleRuntimeIssuesJsonPath);
        string supportBundleRuntimeIssuesMarkdown = SafeReadAllText(supportBundleRuntimeIssuesMarkdownPath);
        string supportBundleTriageActionsCsvReferencePath = ExtractJsonString(supportBundleManifestJson, "triageActionsCsvReferencePath");
        string supportBundleExternalHandoffHashReferencePath = ExtractJsonString(supportBundleManifestJson, "externalHandoffHashReferencePath");
        string supportBundleExternalHandoffZipSha256 = ExtractJsonString(supportBundleManifestJson, "externalHandoffZipSha256");
        string incidentCsv = SafeReadAllText(incidentLogCsvPath);
        string playLogCsv = SafeReadAllText(playLogCsvPath);
        string combinedText = playLogJson + "\n" +
            playLogCsv + "\n" +
            incidentCsv + "\n" +
            summaryJson + "\n" +
            feedbackMarkdown + "\n" +
            surveyJson + "\n" +
            surveyMarkdown + "\n" +
            dashboardHtml + "\n" +
            diagnosticJson + "\n" +
            diagnosticMarkdown + "\n" +
            supportBundleManifestJson + "\n" +
            supportBundleManifestMarkdown + "\n" +
            supportBundleRuntimeIssuesJson + "\n" +
            supportBundleRuntimeIssuesMarkdown;
        bool hasSupportBundleManifest = File.Exists(supportBundleManifestJsonPath) &&
            File.Exists(supportBundleManifestMarkdownPath) &&
            supportBundleManifestJson.Contains("\"fileCount\"") &&
            supportBundleManifestJson.Contains("\"sessionFileCount\"");
        bool supportBundleHasRuntimeIssues = File.Exists(supportBundleRuntimeIssuesJsonPath) &&
            File.Exists(supportBundleRuntimeIssuesMarkdownPath);
        bool supportBundleFilesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath = !ContainsLocalAbsolutePath(supportBundleManifestJson + "\n" +
            supportBundleManifestMarkdown + "\n" +
            supportBundleRuntimeIssuesJson + "\n" +
            supportBundleRuntimeIssuesMarkdown);

        PlaytestSessionAuditRow row = new()
        {
            sessionId = sessionId,
            source = sourceLabel,
            receivedViaSupportBundle = receivedViaSupportBundle,
            supportBundleName = supportBundleName,
            hasSupportBundleManifest = hasSupportBundleManifest,
            supportBundleHasRuntimeIssues = supportBundleHasRuntimeIssues,
            supportBundleFilesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath = supportBundleFilesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath,
            supportBundleTriageActionsCsvReferencePath = supportBundleTriageActionsCsvReferencePath,
            supportBundleExternalHandoffHashReferencePath = supportBundleExternalHandoffHashReferencePath,
            supportBundleExternalHandoffZipSha256 = supportBundleExternalHandoffZipSha256,
            supportBundleHasExternalHandoffHash = !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(supportBundleExternalHandoffZipSha256) &&
                supportBundleExternalHandoffZipSha256.Length == 64 &&
                !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(supportBundleExternalHandoffHashReferencePath),
            hasPlayLogJson = File.Exists(playLogJsonPath),
            hasPlayLogCsv = File.Exists(playLogCsvPath),
            hasIncidentLogCsv = File.Exists(incidentLogCsvPath),
            hasSummaryJson = File.Exists(summaryJsonPath),
            hasFeedbackMarkdown = File.Exists(feedbackMarkdownPath),
            hasSurveyJson = File.Exists(surveyJsonPath),
            hasSurveyMarkdown = File.Exists(surveyMarkdownPath),
            hasDashboardHtml = File.Exists(dashboardPath),
            hasDiagnosticJson = File.Exists(diagnosticJsonPath),
            hasDiagnosticMarkdown = File.Exists(diagnosticMarkdownPath),
            decisionRows = CountCsvDataRows(playLogCsvPath),
            campaignMandateName = FirstNonEmpty(ExtractJsonString(surveyJson, "campaignMandateName"), ExtractJsonString(summaryJson, "campaignMandateName")),
            campaignGrade = FirstNonEmpty(ExtractJsonString(surveyJson, "campaignGrade"), ExtractJsonString(summaryJson, "campaignGrade")),
            campaignScore = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "campaignScore") > 0 ? ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "campaignScore") : ExtractJsonInt(summaryJson, "campaignScore"),
            endingTitle = FirstNonEmpty(ExtractJsonString(surveyJson, "endingTitle"), ExtractJsonString(summaryJson, "endingTitle")),
            difficultyRating = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "difficultyRating"),
            decisionClarityRating = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "decisionClarityRating"),
            resultFairnessRating = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "resultFairnessRating"),
            uiReadabilityRating = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "uiReadabilityRating"),
            priceValueRating = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "priceValueRating"),
            replayRewardValueRating = ExtractJsonInt(surveyJson, "replayRewardValueRating"),
            difficultyTooHigh = ExtractJsonBool(surveyJson, "difficultyTooHigh"),
            uiNeedsWork = ExtractJsonBool(surveyJson, "uiNeedsWork"),
            caseExplanationNeeded = ExtractJsonBool(surveyJson, "caseExplanationNeeded"),
            replayIntent = ExtractJsonBool(surveyJson, "replayIntent"),
            hasCampaignGrade = summaryJson.Contains("\"campaignGrade\"") && summaryJson.Contains("\"campaignScore\""),
            hasNextCampaignObjective = summaryJson.Contains("\"nextCampaignMandateId\"") && summaryJson.Contains("\"nextCampaignChallenge\""),
            hasSurveyRatings = surveyJson.Contains("\"difficultyRating\"") &&
                surveyJson.Contains("\"decisionClarityRating\"") &&
                surveyJson.Contains("\"priceValueRating\""),
            hasDiagnosticFrameSample = diagnosticJson.Contains("\"p95FrameMs\"") &&
                diagnosticJson.Contains("\"sampleFrameCount\"") &&
                diagnosticJson.Contains("\"graphicsDeviceName\""),
            filesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath = !ContainsLocalAbsolutePath(combinedText)
        };

        if (row.replayRewardValueRating <= 0 && row.priceValueRating > 0)
        {
            row.replayRewardValueRating = row.priceValueRating;
        }

        row.complete = row.hasPlayLogJson &&
            row.hasPlayLogCsv &&
            row.hasIncidentLogCsv &&
            row.hasSummaryJson &&
            row.hasFeedbackMarkdown &&
            row.hasSurveyJson &&
            row.hasSurveyMarkdown &&
            row.hasDashboardHtml &&
            row.hasDiagnosticJson &&
            row.hasDiagnosticMarkdown &&
            row.decisionRows >= 35 &&
            row.hasCampaignGrade &&
            row.hasNextCampaignObjective &&
            row.hasSurveyRatings &&
            row.hasDiagnosticFrameSample &&
            (!row.receivedViaSupportBundle ||
                (row.hasSupportBundleManifest &&
                    row.supportBundleHasRuntimeIssues &&
                    row.supportBundleFilesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath)) &&
            row.filesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath;
        row.notes = BuildPlaytestSessionAuditNotes(row);
        return row;
    }

    private static string FindSupportBundleRoot(string sessionPath)
    {
        DirectoryInfo current = Directory.Exists(sessionPath) ? new DirectoryInfo(sessionPath) : null;
        while (current != null)
        {
            if (File.Exists(Path.Combine(current.FullName, "care_review_support_bundle_manifest.json")) ||
                current.Name.StartsWith("care_review_support_bundle_", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
            {
                return current.FullName;
            }

            current = current.Parent;
        }

        return "";
    }

    private static string BuildPlaytestSessionAuditNotes(PlaytestSessionAuditRow row)
    {
        List<string> notes = new();
        if (row.decisionRows < 35)
        {
            notes.Add("decision_rows_below_35");
        }

        if (!row.hasSurveyJson || !row.hasSurveyMarkdown || !row.hasSurveyRatings)
        {
            notes.Add("survey_missing_or_incomplete");
        }

        if (!row.hasDiagnosticJson || !row.hasDiagnosticMarkdown || !row.hasDiagnosticFrameSample)
        {
            notes.Add("diagnostic_missing_or_incomplete");
        }

        if (row.receivedViaSupportBundle && !row.hasSupportBundleManifest)
        {
            notes.Add("support_bundle_manifest_missing");
        }

        if (row.receivedViaSupportBundle && !row.supportBundleHasRuntimeIssues)
        {
            notes.Add("support_bundle_runtime_issues_missing");
        }

        if (row.receivedViaSupportBundle && !row.supportBundleFilesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath)
        {
            notes.Add("support_bundle_local_absolute_path_found");
        }

        if (row.receivedViaSupportBundle && !row.supportBundleHasExternalHandoffHash)
        {
            notes.Add("support_bundle_external_handoff_hash_missing");
        }

        if (!row.hasCampaignGrade)
        {
            notes.Add("campaign_grade_missing");
        }

        if (!row.hasNextCampaignObjective)
        {
            notes.Add("next_campaign_missing");
        }

        if (!row.filesHaveNoLocalAbsolutePath)
        {
            notes.Add("local_absolute_path_found");
        }

        return notes.Count == 0 ? "ok" : string.Join(";", notes);
    }

    private static int CountCsvDataRows(string path)
    {
        if (!File.Exists(path))
        {
            return 0;
        }

        int lineCount = 0;
        foreach (string line in File.ReadLines(path, Encoding.UTF8))
        {
            if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(line))
            {
                lineCount++;
            }
        }

        return Math.Max(0, lineCount - 1);
    }

